 that would be bad, these shrooms kick my ass hardcore style.  (Supernal Elixir owns btw).  I'm doing it as fast as possible without getting attacked alot.<br>
<br>
Having said that, with the epic pet, I think you could easily get 1 aaxp per 3 hours because the epic pet would OWN these shrooms even more than a focus staffed 57 earth pet does, and he REALLY owns them.<br>
<br>
the ONLY con to this zone is you have to be level 60 or higher to single pull the shrooms.  so unless your 60 you cant come here unless you also have a friend with a 60+ who you can 2 box to pull for you.  hehe.<br>
<br>
BTW, i'm level 60.  I think at 61, these shrooms MIGHT light blue out, can anyone confirm that or not?  I think they are level 46 which should LB at 61<br>
